text:
Dior reinvents its iconic spa at the Hôtel Plaza Athénée in Paris, giving it a new setting designed as the ultimate Parisian sanctuary for well-being.

Located at the heart of Avenue Montaigne, Hôtel Plaza Athénée and Christian Dior share a rich heritage. Dior Spa Plaza Athénée offers exclusive experiences, featuring Dior Powered by Hydrafacial and 'Cronos light' in the Dior Light Suite, inspired by light therapy with LED-embedded ceilings for revitalization, relaxation, or restoration.

© Matthieu Salvaing

text:

© Andrea Cenetiempo

text:
In the sixth decade of a prolific career, during which she has been a key second-wave feminist figure, Judy Chicago is the latest inspiring woman to incarnate the 'Dior Lady 95.22' by Maria Grazia Chiuri on.dior.com/lady-95.22. As her major survey 'Herstory' supported by Dior opens at New York’s New Museum, she opens up about finding fulfillment in daily life, the drive that propelled her to succeed as an artist in spite of the patriarchal power structure of the time, and her conviction that real style results from being true to oneself.
© Brigitte Lacombe

text: Having collaborated with the House on several occasions, Judy Chicago now joins the circle of women embodying the 'Dior Lady 95.22' by Maria Grazia Chiuri on.dior.com/lady-9522. The American artist highlights the contemporary nature of this interpretation of the Lady Dior bag's iconic architecture by wearing it crossbody, highlighting the juxtaposition of its softly rounded forms and the high-tech mix of Macro and Maxicannage quilted contrasts. The Medium black format shown is one of three sizes and two color options, available in select boutiques worldwide.

text:

Distinguished by a retro allure, and featuring the "CD" initials revealed in Dior Oblique jacquard, these objects of desire combine elegance, a sportswear spirit, and virtuoso savoir-faire, with a range of styles to choose from, sublimated by bewitching colors such as gray, black, blue, red, beige or cream. © We Are From LA

text:
Dior is pleased to announce Mélanie de Jesus dos Santos as its new ambassador for the Olympic Games Paris 2024, with LVMH a Premium Partner of the event. Pictured in Dior looks by Maria Grazia Chiuri, the French athlete, a four-time European champion in artistic gymnastics, embodies the same values of audacity, creativity and excellence dear to Christian Dior.

Dans le prolongement du partenariat d’exception signé avec LVMH, Dior a le plaisir d'annoncer Mélanie de Jesus dos Santos comme nouvelle ambassadrice pour les Jeux Olympiques de Paris 2024. Vêtue ici de looks Dior imaginés par Maria Grazia Chiuri, l'athlète française, quadruple championne d'Europe de gymnastique artistique, incarne les mêmes valeurs d'audace, de créativité et d'excellence, chères à Christian Dior.

© Nelson Rosier

text:
LVMH and Dior are proud to support Mélanie de Jesus dos Santos, four-time European champion, towards Paris 2024 and welcome her into the LVMH family.🏅

As part of the partnership between Paris 2024 and LVMH, the Group and its Maisons aim at providing direct support for certain athletes whose exemplary journeys make them ‘Artisans of All Victories’.

Mélanie de Jesus dos Santos will represent Christian Dior as an ambassador for the Olympic Games Paris 2024. Driven by the same values of audacity, creativity and excellence, dear to Monsieur Christian Dior, Mélanie de Jesus dos Santos shapes her dream every day: an Olympic medal in Paris.

Learn More: https://www.lvmh.com/news-documents/news/paris-2024%e2%80%afolympic-games-lvmh-and-dior-are-proud-to-welcome-melanie-de-jesus-dos-santos-to-the-lvmh-family/

-\-\

LVMH et Dior sont fiers de soutenir Mélanie de Jesus dos Santos, quatre fois championne d'Europe, pour Paris 2024 et de l'accueillir dans la famille LVMH.🏅

Dans le cadre du partenariat entre Paris 2024 et LVMH, le Groupe et ses Maisons ont à coeur de soutenir directement certains athlètes, dont le parcours est exemplaire et fait d’eux des Artisans de Toutes les Victoires.

Mélanie de Jesus dos Santos représentera en tant qu'ambassadeur la Maison Christian Dior pour les Jeux Olympiques de Paris 2024. Animée des mêmes valeurs d'audace, de créativité et d'excellence, chères à Monsieur Christian Dior, Mélanie de Jesus dos Santos façonne chaque jour son rêve : une médaille olympique à Paris.

En savoir plus: https://www.lvmh.fr/actualites-documents/actualites/jeux-olympiques-de-paris-2024%e2%80%af-lvmh-et-dior-sont-fiers-daccueillir-melanie-de-jesus-dos-santos-dans-la-famille-lvmh/

#LVMH #Dior #ArtisanDeToutesLesVictoires

text:
A peek backstage before the Spring-Summer 2024 show highlights some of the stand-out details from the new collection on.dior.com/ss2024 by Maria Grazia Chiuri. The predominance of black boasts interplays between sheer lace and shoulder-baring shirts and dresses, contrasted by the graphic luxuriant leather of 'Dior Toujours', 'Lady Dior' and 'Lady D-Joy' bags. The botanical and cosmic motifs that illuminate clothing also make their way onto the 'Dior Book Tote' as well as chokers and cuffs.
© Elena Dottelonde

Under Peter Philips Makeup’s vision, Dior’s signature no-transfer formula reveals a new side of intense luminosity, in a glossy midnight blue bottle. Achieve a spectacular shiny lip look in one swipe, ensuring extraordinary 12H wear and comfort.

Available in 8 bold shades from red to nude.

text:
Nestled on the mountainside, amidst the splendor of Provençal Drôme, in France, a group of men and women gracefully bend over, sickles in hand, engaging in the timeless tradition of lavender harvesting.

With reverence, they gather the wild lavender that grows in scattered bushes, embracing the essence of this altitude plant, emanating a truly unique aroma. This unique Lavender Blue-Gold, known as "true" lavender, thrives responsibly in this region and only a few growers still pick it in the traditional way.

#DiorBeauty #DiorParfums

text:
Crafting the essence of lavender.

Meet Philippe Soguel, French lavender distiller and long-time House partner.

With a passion for Provence's botanical treasures, ‘Bleu Provence’ a company led by Philippe Soguel since 1994, thrives on modesty and excellence. Hand in hand with local producers, they preserve heritage and develop organic crops.

Pioneering environmental advancements, their lavender harvesters protect nature's beauty while crafting tailor-made excellence for Dior.

#DiorBeauty #DiorParfums
